data.description: LOCATION IS THE WORD OF THE DAY! A rocks throw to the up & coming Frederickson area, minutes to 512, I-5, the Sounders Train, JBLM, all the restaurants, shopping, schools, entertainment & the added bonus of the Frederickson Community center is right here. This 3 story (END UNIT) Fountain Park Condo (entry on the ground floor) is warm, spacious & inviting. The great room greets you w/an eat in kitchen (ALL appliances stay) dining room, 1/2 bath, balcony, lots of storage & that's just the main floor. Before I go to the top floor, there is a tandem 2 car garage w/an additional work space on the ground floor as well! Up to the top floor we go, you have 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths, the primary suit & the laundry room. Pets welcome, walking trails.
